title: Mogoze v1.9 - Responsive Magazine WordPress Theme
description:
Mogoze Magazine WordPress Theme was created with love using the latest HTML5 and CSS3 techniques with a validity code, completely responsive to look perfectly in all mobile devices, easily usable with any device as well as PCs. Responsive design optimized for tablets and smartphones (resize browser and hit refresh to check it out).

- Super Fast! Created with love using the latest HTML5 and CSS3 techniques with a validity code, completely responsive! Mogoze has been optimised to the maximum, to give you one of the best Magazine Themes!


- Blog Posts Unlimited image for the gallery slider format with drag and drop! With meta boxes for videos Youtube & Vimeo.

- Custom Post Types Mogoze has custom post types for FAQs and Jobs, this makes it easier to keep your content organized.

- Translation Ready You can translate the Theme to your own language. The theme includes .po & .mo files for easy translation.

- Easy Setup .XML File This theme includes a .xml file that will allow you to import the sample data to your site.

Product page: http://themeforest.net/item/mogoze-responsive-magazine-wordpress-theme/6319860

This wordpress theme has been fully nulled, to install simply upload it to your host like you would any other wordpress theme.
